---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About | AZea Labs"
  description="Learn more about AZea Labs, a software development and QA automation ecosystem created by Antonio Zea."
  canonicalPath="/about"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-white/10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(59,130,246,0.24),transparent_35%),radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_left,rgba(14,165,233,0.14),transparent_30%)]"></div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-8">
        <header class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <a href="/" class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight">
            AZea<span class="text-sky-400">Labs</span>
          </a>

          <nav class="hidden items-center gap-6 text-sm text-slate-300 md:flex">
            <a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Home</a>
            <a href="/about" class="text-white">About</a>
            <a href="/#projects" class="hover:text-white">Projects</a>
            <a href="/#contact" class="hover:text-white">Contact</a>
          </nav>
        </header>

        <div class="py-24 md:py-32">
          <p class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-sky-400/30 bg-sky-400/10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-sky-300">
            About AZea Labs
          </p>

          <h1 class="mt-6 max-w-4xl text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-7xl">
            Building a professional ecosystem around software, automation, and learning.
          </h1>

          <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300">
            AZea Labs is a long-term software and QA automation ecosystem
            created by Antonio Zea. It starts as a professional portfolio, but
            its purpose is bigger: to build real products, document technical
            decisions, improve development skills, and create practical tools
            for automation engineers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
      <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr]">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sky-400">
            Mission
          </p>
          <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl">
            Learn by building. Teach by understanding.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-slate-300">
          <p>
            The mission of AZea Labs is to create a practical bridge between
            QA automation, software development, architecture, and technical
            education. Instead of only studying concepts in isolation, AZea Labs
            focuses on building real projects that can be used, tested,
            improved, documented, and eventually taught.
          </p>

          <p>
            The ecosystem is designed to grow step by step: first as a
            portfolio, then as a QA automation practice platform, and later as
            a foundation for courses, examples, APIs, tools, and future
            software products.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-y border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03]">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sky-400">
          Professional Focus
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl">
          Focused on QA automation, software quality, and modern development.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">QA Automation</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">
              Experience and continuous learning around UI automation, API
              testing, test design, selectors, maintainability, and automation
              frameworks.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Software Development</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">
              Building projects with modern frontend and backend technologies
              while improving architecture, clean structure, and deployment
              practices.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Technical Education</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">
              Creating resources, examples, and future learning paths for
              automation engineers who want practical, realistic, and
              structured learning.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sky-400">
            Creator
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold text-white">
            Antonio Zea
          </h2>

          <p class="mt-5 text-slate-300">
            Antonio Zea is a QA Automation professional focused on building
            stronger technical skills across automation, development,
            architecture, and software delivery. AZea Labs is his public
            platform for building real projects, documenting progress, and
            turning technical learning into practical products.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sky-400">
            Direction
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold text-white">
            From portfolio to ecosystem
          </h2>

          <p class="mt-5 text-slate-300">
            AZea Labs will evolve beyond a personal website. The roadmap
            includes QA Labs, automation examples, API practice scenarios,
            technical documentation, future academy content, and additional
            software projects connected by the same professional identity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-y border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03]">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sky-400">
          Principles
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl">
          The principles behind AZea Labs.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Build in public</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">
              Progress should be visible, documented, and connected to real
              outcomes. Each project is an opportunity to improve technical
              judgment and execution.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Practice over theory alone</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">
              Concepts become stronger when they are applied to real projects,
              real code, real tests, real documentation, and real deployment
              workflows.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Automation-friendly design</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">
              Software should be designed with quality and testability in mind:
              stable selectors, predictable flows, useful APIs, and clear
              documentation.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Professional evolution</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">
              AZea Labs is a long-term path to grow from QA automation into
              stronger software development, architecture, teaching, and product
              thinking.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/80 p-8 md:p-12">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sky-400">
          Next
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl">
          The next major product is QA Labs.
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-slate-300">
          QA Labs will be a practice platform for automation engineers, designed
          with web UI scenarios, API testing, stable selectors, documentation,
          and examples across multiple automation tools.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <a
            href="/projects/qalabs"
            class="rounded-lg bg-sky-400 px-6 py-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 transition hover:bg-sky-300"
          >
            View QA Labs
          </a>

          <a
            href="/#contact"
            class="rounded-lg border border-white/15 px-6 py-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-white/10"
          >
            Contact
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>